## 2. Typography & Spacing

- The default font for all body and UI text is **Inter** for a modern, professional look.

### Headings
| Level   | Size    | Weight   |
|---------|---------|----------|
| h1      | 2.25rem | Bold     |
| h2      | 1.875rem| Bold     |
| h3      | 1.5rem  | Semibold |
| h4      | 1.25rem | Semibold |
| h5      | 1.125rem| Medium   |
| h6      | 1rem    | Medium   |

### Body Text
- **Base:** 1rem (16px), regular weight
- **Muted:** Use `text-muted` or `text-muted-foreground`

### Spacing Scale
- **xs:** 0.25rem (4px)
- **sm:** 0.5rem (8px)
- **md:** 1rem (16px)
- **lg:** 1.5rem (24px)
- **xl:** 2rem (32px)
- Use Tailwind spacing utilities for margin/padding (e.g., `p-4`, `mt-2`)

