## 4. Accessibility & Responsiveness

- **Color contrast:** All text and interactive elements must meet WCAG AA contrast ratios.
- **Focus states:** Use visible focus rings (`focus-visible:ring-*`).
- **Scaling:** Components must be usable on mobile and desktop (min touch target: 44x44px).
- **Font scaling:** Use `rem` units and responsive Tailwind classes (e.g., `text-lg md:text-xl`).

